-- â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
function Library:AddWindow(title, cfg)
    cfg = cfg or {}
    local theme    = Themes[cfg.theme or "Dark"]
    local winSize  = cfg.size or Vector2.new(560, 420)
    local minKey   = cfg.toggle_key or Enum.KeyCode.RightShift
    local SIDEBAR  = 140
    local TITLEH   = 42

    -- ScreenGui
    local sg = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
    sg.Name = "FluentUI_" .. title
    sg.ZIndexBehavior = Enum.ZIndexBehavior.Sibling
    sg.ResetOnSpawn = false
    sg.Parent = (pcall(function() return CoreGui end) and CoreGui) or Players.LocalPlayer:WaitForChild("PlayerGui")

    -- Ventana principal
    local mainFrame = Frame({
        Name = "Window",
        Size = UDim2.fromOffset(winSize.X, winSize.Y),
        Position = UDim2.fromOffset(
            math.floor((workspace.CurrentCamera.ViewportSize.X - winSize.X) / 2),
            math.floor((workspace.CurrentCamera.ViewportSize.Y - winSize.Y) / 2)
        ),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Background,
        ClipsDescendants = true,
    }, sg)
    Corner(10, mainFrame)

    -- Borde exterior sutil
    local stroke = Instance.new("UIStroke")
    stroke.Color = theme.BorderLine
    stroke.Thickness = 1
    stroke.Transparency = 0
    stroke.Parent = mainFrame

    -- â”€â”€ TitleBar â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
    local titleBar = Frame({
        Name = "TitleBar",
        Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, TITLEH),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.TitleBar,
        ZIndex = 2,
    }, mainFrame)

    -- LÃ­nea inferior del titleBar
    Frame({
        Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 1),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, 0, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Separator,
    }, titleBar)

    -- Ãcono cuadrado de acento
    local accentBar = Frame({
        Size = UDim2.fromOffset(4, 20),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, 12, 0.5, -10),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Accent,
    }, titleBar)
    Corner(2, accentBar)

    -- TÃ­tulo
    Label({
        Text = title,
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -120, 1, 0),
        Position = UDim2.fromOffset(24, 0),
        TextColor3 = theme.Text,
        Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextSize = 14,
        ZIndex = 3,
    }, titleBar)

    -- SubtÃ­tulo (opcional)
    if cfg.subtitle then
        Label({
            Text = cfg.subtitle,
            Size = UDim2.new(0.4, 0, 1, 0),
            Position = UDim2.new(0, 24 + 120, 0, 0),
            TextColor3 = theme.TextDim,
            Font = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextSize = 11,
            ZIndex = 3,
        }, titleBar)
    end

    -- BotÃ³n minimizar/cerrar
    local function mkBarBtn(icon, xOff, onClick)
        local btn = Button({
            Text = icon,
            Size = UDim2.fromOffset(26, 26),
            Position = UDim2.new(1, xOff, 0.5, -13),
            BackgroundColor3 = theme.ElementBg,
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            TextColor3 = theme.TextMuted,
            Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
            TextSize = 13,
            ZIndex = 5,
        }, titleBar)
        Corner(6, btn)
        btn.MouseEnter:Connect(function()   Tween(btn, {BackgroundTransparency = 0.3}) end)
        btn.MouseLeave:Connect(function()   Tween(btn, {BackgroundTransparency = 1})   end)
        btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(onClick)
        return btn
    end

    mkBarBtn("âœ•", -10, function()
        Tween(mainFrame, {Size = UDim2.fromOffset(winSize.X, 0)}, 0.2)
        task.delay(0.22, function() sg:Destroy() end)
    end)
    local minimized = false
    mkBarBtn("â”€", -40, function()
        minimized = not minimized
        if minimized then
            Tween(mainFrame, {Size = UDim2.fromOffset(winSize.X, TITLEH)}, 0.2)
        else
            Tween(mainFrame, {Size = UDim2.fromOffset(winSize.X, winSize.Y)}, 0.2)
        end
    end)

    -- â”€â”€ Dragging â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
    do
        local dragging, dragStart, startPos
        titleBar.InputBegan:Connect(function(inp)
            if inp.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 then
                dragging = true
                dragStart = inp.Position
                startPos  = mainFrame.Position
            end
        end)
        UIS.InputChanged:Connect(function(inp)
            if dragging and inp.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseMovement then
                local delta = inp.Position - dragStart
                mainFrame.Position = UDim2.fromOffset(
                    startPos.X.Offset + delta.X,
                    startPos.Y.Offset + delta.Y
                )
            end
        end)
        UIS.InputEnded:Connect(function(inp)
            if inp.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 then
                dragging = false
            end
        end)
    end

    -- Toggle tecla
    UIS.InputBegan:Connect(function(inp, gpe)
        if not gpe and inp.KeyCode == minKey then
            sg.Enabled = not sg.Enabled
        end
    end)

    -- â”€â”€ Sidebar â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
    local sidebar = Frame({
        Name = "Sidebar",
        Size = UDim2.new(0, SIDEBAR, 1, -TITLEH),
        Position = UDim2.fromOffset(0, TITLEH),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Sidebar,
    }, mainFrame)

    -- LÃ­nea derecha sidebar
    Frame({
        Size = UDim2.new(0, 1, 1, 0),
        Position = UDim2.new(1, -1, 0, 0),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Separator,
    }, sidebar)

    local tabBtnList = Scroll({
        Name = "TabBtnScroll",
        Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, -10),
        Position = UDim2.fromOffset(0, 8),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0),
        ScrollBarImageColor3 = theme.Scrollbar,
    }, sidebar)
    List(Enum.FillDirection.Vertical, 4, tabBtnList)
    Pad(0, 0, 8, 8, tabBtnList)

    -- â”€â”€ Content area â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
    local contentArea = Frame({
        Name = "Content",
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -SIDEBAR, 1, -TITLEH),
        Position = UDim2.fromOffset(SIDEBAR, TITLEH),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Surface,
    }, mainFrame)

    -- â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
    --  TABS MANAGER
    -- â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
    local Tabs = {}
    local activeTab = nil
    local tabCount = 0

    local function autoCanvasY(scrollFrame, listLayout)
        listLayout:GetPropertyChangedSignal("AbsoluteContentSize"):Connect(function()
            scrollFrame.CanvasSize = UDim2.fromOffset(0, listLayout.AbsoluteContentSize.Y + 12)
        end)
    end

    function Tabs:AddTab(tabTitle, icon)
        tabCount = tabCount + 1
        local order = tabCount

        -- BotÃ³n en sidebar
        local tabBtn = Button({
            Text = "",
            Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 34),
            BackgroundColor3 = theme.ElementBg,
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            LayoutOrder = order,
        }, tabBtnList)
        Corner(8, tabBtn)

        -- Barra de acento izquierda (activo)
        local accentLine = Frame({
            Size = UDim2.fromOffset(3, 18),
            Position = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0.5, -9),
            BackgroundColor3 = theme.Accent,
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        }, tabBtn)
        Corner(2, accentLine)

        -- Ãcono (opcional, texto simple)
        if icon then
            Label({
                Text = icon,
                Size = UDim2.fromOffset(18, 34),
                Position = UDim2.fromOffset(10, 0),
                TextColor3 = theme.TextMuted,
                Font = Enum.Font.GothamSemibold,
                TextSize = 13,
                TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Center,
            }, tabBtn)
        end

        -- Texto del tab
        local tabLabel = Label({
            Text = tabTitle,
            Size = UDim2.new(1, icon and -36 or -16, 1, 0),
            Position = UDim2.fromOffset(icon and 32 or 12, 0),
            TextColor3 = theme.TextMuted,
            Font = Enum.Font.GothamSemibold,
            TextSize = 13,
        }, tabBtn)

        -- Contenido del tab
        local tabContent = Scroll({
            Name = "Tab_" .. tabTitle,
            Size = UDim2.fromScale(1, 1),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0),
            ScrollBarImageColor3 = theme.Scrollbar,
            Visible = false,
        }, contentArea)
        local contentList = List(Enum.FillDirection.Vertical, 6, tabContent)
        Pad(10, 10, 12, 12, tabContent)
        autoCanvasY(tabContent, contentList)

        -- Activate tab
        local function activate()
            if activeTab then
                -- Desactivar tab anterior
                activeTab._content.Visible = false
                Tween(activeTab._btn, {BackgroundTransparency = 1})
                Tween(activeTab._label, {TextColor3 = theme.TextMuted})
                Tween(activeTab._accent, {BackgroundTransparency = 1})
            end
            activeTab = {
                _content = tabContent,
                _btn     = tabBtn,
                _label   = tabLabel,
                _accent  = accentLine,
            }
            tabContent.Visible = true
            Tween(tabBtn, {BackgroundTransparency = 0.85})
            Tween(tabLabel, {TextColor3 = theme.Text})
            Tween(accentLine, {BackgroundTransparency = 0})
        end

        tabBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(activate)
        tabBtn.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
            if activeTab and activeTab._btn ~= tabBtn then
                Tween(tabBtn, {BackgroundTransparency = 0.92})
            end
        end)
        tabBtn.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
            if activeTab and activeTab._btn ~= tabBtn then
                Tween(tabBtn, {BackgroundTransparency = 1})
            end
        end)

        if tabCount == 1 then activate() end

        -- â”€â”€ Elementos del Tab â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
        local Tab = {}

        -- Helper: contenedor base de elemento
        local function mkElement(extraH)
            extraH = extraH or 0
            local el = Frame({
                Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 40 + extraH),
                BackgroundColor3 = theme.ElementBg,
            }, tabContent)
            Corner(8, el)
            local stroke2 = Instance.new("UIStroke")
            stroke2.Color = theme.Separator
            stroke2.Thickness = 1
            stroke2.Transparency = 0.5
            stroke2.Parent = el
            return el
        end

        -- â”€â”€ LABEL â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
        function Tab:AddLabel(text)
            local el = mkElement()
            el.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 30)
            Label({
                Text = text,
                Size = UDim2.new(1, -20, 1, 0),
                Position = UDim2.fromOffset(12, 0),
                TextColor3 = theme.TextMuted,
                Font = Enum.Font.Gotham,
                TextSize = 12,
            }, el)
            return el
        end

        -- â”€â”€ BUTTON â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
        function Tab:AddButton(text, callback)
            callback = callback or function() end
            local el = mkElement()
            Label({
                Text = text,
                Size = UDim2.new(1, -110, 1, 0),
                Position = UDim2.fromOffset(14, 0),
